      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. i'm mostly just worried about the pain keeping me up. i have some oxycodone left over from a dental thing last year though, would it be okay if i took one of those? it would definitely help me sleep better than the ibuprofen would. i really don't want to go to the hospital if i don't have to, it's such a hassle.",
